title: WoW Zygor's Guide 1-80 (2/24/09 Update)
description:
The wonderful leveling addon by Zygor. This is the 2/24/09 Update for both Horde and Alliance. 

Simply put the "ZygorGuidesViewer", "ZygorGuidesAllaince" and "ZygorGuidesHorde" folders into you WoW/Interface/Addons folder. 

Official Site: http://www.zygorguides.com/

Forum Post for 2/24 Update: http://www.zygorguides.com/forum/showthread.php?t=1509

Please seed and keep the latest versions coming :D
